<div class="container"
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #333;">
    <h1 style="text-align: center; color: #4CAF50;">Welcome to Our Franchise
        Network!</h1>
    <h3>Franchise Details</h3>
    <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= leadName %></p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= leadEmail %></p>
    <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= leadPhone %></p>

    <p>We’re excited to have you join our franchise network. Please click the
        link below to create your password and set up your account:</p>

    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
        <a href="<%= passwordCreateLink %>"
            style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px; color: white; background-color: #4CAF50; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
            Create Your Password
        </a>
    </p>

    <p>If the button above doesn’t work, you can copy and paste the following
        link into your browser:</p>
    <p><a href="<%= passwordCreateLink %>"><%= passwordCreateLink %></a></p>

    <div class="footer"
        style="margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 10px;">
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #777;">
            Follow up promptly to complete your setup. Welcome to the team!
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
